  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Given the 100 fold increase of the incidence of Pompe's disease in Western French Guiana, the
      objective of the present study is to implement systematic screening in newborns in French
      Guiana in order to start treatment before the muscular and cardiac symptoms appear.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
